</p>
<p>Execute Behat to get that definition printed out for us:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:21</div></code></pre>
<p>When you're feeling <em>really</em> lazy, you can add a <code>--append-snippets</code> flag and Behat
will put the definitions inside of the <code>FeatureContext</code> class for you:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/product_admin.feature:21 --append-snippets</div></code></pre>
<p>Change <code>arg1</code> to be <code>rowText</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="d7f998cd64">
